{
  "doc_id": "2618",
  "text": "Sequence-based identification of Phytophthora species is now widely used, and identification using online tools such as GenBank, the Phytophthora database, or Phytophthora-ID have been developed [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The pitfalls of sequence-based identifications have been recently reviewed [CITATION_3] . Species identification cannot rely solely on sequence-based identification, since some of the sequence data present in GenBank and elsewhere may not have been submitted for morphologically well-characterized Phytophthora species.",
